			<outline text="August 13" type="calendarDay" name="13" >
				<outline text="Looking at new TVs. Q: can optical audio-out of a TV be volume-controllable with the TV's remote? Our cheap 1K Samsung is not. The volume is fixed. But is the level (volume) controllable with other optical-out TVs? Thanks!" type="tweet" created="Fri, 13 Aug 2021 22:00:13 GMT" tweetId="1426302597317767170" urltweet="https://twitter.com/dsearls/status/1426302597317767170" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="dsearls" />
				<outline text="What is the cheapest and easiest approach to steadily backing up two Mac laptops with a total of ~10TB of data between them, using Time Machine?" type="tweet" created="Fri, 13 Aug 2021 12:49:18 GMT" tweetId="1426163956855492609" urltweet="https://twitter.com/dsearls/status/1426163956855492609" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="dsearls" />
