				<outline text="When my phone looks at the QR code on desktop @signalapp, it says &quot;No usable data found.&quot; Also, do these directions under the QR code mean Signal Settings in the phone's settings for Signal, or settings in the Signal app on the phone? I don't see either. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/dsearls/status/1412399194237767681/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 06 Jul 2021 13:13:03 GMT" tweetId="1412399194237767681" urltweet="https://twitter.com/dsearls/status/1412399194237767681" tweetUserName="dsearls" />
