			<outline text="July 2" type="calendarDay" name="02" >
				<outline text="Follow this @google #streetview: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps/@50.2298044,-121.581646,3a,75y,9.21h,89.45t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1seo6hwTGmRCRaiGkEPgnnAA!2e0!7i13312!8i6656?shorturl=1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; All of that is gone. Sympathies from California, where our home has come close to this twice so far. https://t.co/Zch552MSTv" type="tweet" created="Sat, 03 Jul 2021 01:57:01 GMT" tweetId="1411141901185650689" urltweet="https://twitter.com/dsearls/status/1411141901185650689" tweetUserName="dsearls" />
				<outline text="Not a thread, but perhaps a thing: better #epitaphs
To get started: 
&quot;I was almost finished&quot; 
