				<outline text="I just re-logged in to Twitter through my @digime app. The flag @twitter sent me to review the login said I was in Staten Island rather than at the north end of Manhattan. This is no big deal, but does identify a feature of (rather than a bug in) how the Net's innards work." type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 13:38:13 GMT" tweetId="1409506422463860737" urltweet="https://twitter.com/dsearls/status/1409506422463860737" tweetUserName="dsearls" />
